data.description: A 3-bedroom home on 5 acres of land offers plenty of space and opportunities for country living with beautiful country views. With a circular driveway, you'll have easy access to and from your property. The home features 2 living areas with 2 fireplaces and a spacious kitchen with an island for more counterspace. The inclusion of county water and sewer services ensures convenience and eliminates the need for a well or septic system. Experience the benefits of no HOA with only minimal Deed Restrictions. The 5-acre plot allows so many opportunities for your own dreams to come to fruition. Live in a country setting while close to the city limits as well. Don't miss this opportunity!
